box-shadow: x y;
box-shadow: x y color;
box-shadow: x y blur color;
box-shadow: x y blur spreadRadius color;
box-shadow: x y blur color, x y blur color, x y blur color; //Multiple shadows
box-shadow: x y blur color inset; //sombra dentro do elemento

exemplo "polaroid" picture: https://www.w3schools.com/cssref/css3_pr_box-shadow.asp
